    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 72-77.</p><p>Persistent Arcanum</p><p>Starting at 21st level, you gain a deeper understanding of the functioning of your pact magic. You gain an additional 5th level spell slot (included on the class table).</p><p>When you complete a short rest, you regain any expended uses of your 6th and 7th-level Mystic Arcanums. In addition, you learn one additional Mystic Arcanum option for each Mystic Arcanum up to 9th level. When you cast a Mystic Arcanum, you can choose either option.</p></div>",
